Our weekly report compares spot- based valuation, cash flow and earnings metrics to current consensus and our base- case values for all stocks under our coverage.

We compile the "Spot Base Consensus" report on a weekly basis to display spot price scenario outcomes. All other assumptions from our base- case models are unchanged. This provides context for current equity and commodity prices. The charts and tables below display the scenario outcomes.

Methodology: We run spot commodity and currency prices through our models up to CY31, then switch to our longer- term base case price assumptions detailed here - metal&ROCK: The Price Deck - 3Q25: Tariffs, China and the USD (14 Jul 2025)

Source: Refinitiv consensus estimate Morgan Stanley Research.
